@startuml auth-flow
!theme plain

title Authentication & Authorization Flow (AppWrite)

actor "Client\n(ExtJS/Mobile)" as C
participant "AppWrite\n(Auth v1.3.4)" as AW
participant "Mail Service" as MS

C -> AW : Login\nPOST /v1/account/sessions/email\n{email, password}
AW --> C : JWT Token + Session

note right of AW
  AppWrite v1.3.4
  Self-hosted
  JWT claims:
  userId, empId, posId
end note

C -> MS : Request\nAuthorization: Bearer {jwt}

MS -> MS : JWT Filter\n- Validate token with AppWrite SDK\n- Extract: userId, empId, posId, roles

MS --> C : Response

@enduml
